{"tid":1892400,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[信你一成]  與北京建交後 所羅門將獲千億美元貸款","createTime":"2020-02-22T13:29:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T22:10:57.000Z","uid":141151,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"055c2aa806f324f0bc7a6a817414175f4866164c","tid":1892400,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:29:32.000Z","msg":"與北京建交後 所羅門將獲千億美元貸款<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94-%E8%88%87%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%BB%BA%E4%BA%A4%E5%BE%8C-%E6%89%80%E7%BE%85%E9%96%80%E5%B0%87%E7%8D%B2%E5%8D%83%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE-121300248.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25AA%2592%25E9%25AB%2594-%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E5%25BE%258C-%25E6%2589%2580%25E7%25BE%2585%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%25B0%2587%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%258D%2583%25E5%2584%2584%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2585%2583%25E8%25B2%25B8%25E6%25AC%25BE-121300248.html&d=l2jL6rfoxymyXK22uA%2BdgoICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=76ed4dde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94-%E8%88%87%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%BB%BA%E4%BA%A4%E5%BE%8C-%E6%89%80%E7%BE%85%E9%96%80%E5%B0%87%E7%8D%B2%E5%8D%83%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE-121300248.html</a><br />\n<br />\n（德國之聲中文網）在與台灣斷交，轉投北京&quot;懷抱&quot;之後，所羅門群島有望從中國那裡獲得1000億美元貸款。這個南太平洋島國的財政部長庫瑪（Harry Kuma）周五拒絕對此消息予以正面表態，而是請求外界等待預計下周會發布的公告。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">路透社得以查看的一份政府內部文件，則顯示了相關交易的細節內容：&quot;身份保密的出資方&quot;將會通過北京的金融中介商Terry Wong提供1000億美元。這筆貸款金額相當於所羅門群島經濟總量的大約66倍。<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n所羅門群島人口約65萬，去年的經濟總產值在14.7億美元左右。<br />\n<br />\n據該國財政部一名內部人士透露，貸款是由&quot;中國的私人出資方&quot;提供的。中國政府並未參與其中。中國外交部在回復路透社相關問詢時表示，對此事並不知情，同時也指出在兩國正式建交之後，雙邊關系發展開了一個好頭。<br />\n<br />\n2019年，所羅門群島和台灣斷絕外交關系，緊接著和北京建立了正式外交關系。美國對這一做法予以激烈批評。<br />\n<br />\n中國政府視台灣為自己的分離省份，認為其不應該和其它國家建立外交關系。所羅門群島此前一直是台灣的長期伙伴，但是卻在2019年秋轉投北京懷抱。<br />\n<br />\n路透社查閱到的這份有關貸款交易的文件上標注的日期是2019年11月，也就是和北京建交之後不久。台灣方面稱，中國不斷地試圖以條件優厚的貸款和其它財政支持作為誘餌，鼓動台灣的邦交國與台北斷交。<br />\n<br />\n雨涵/王凡（路透社）<br />\n<br />\n邊Q個TERRY WONG 有能力借1000億美元俾所羅門群島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要係GDP 66倍，世界上邊個國家承受得起"},{"pid":"6b667f3776f5fe58615181f70ed5e19549616fbf","tid":1892400,"uid":242605,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:29:58.000Z","msg":"麻煩各位手足幫手推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nYouTube 戰線認真要打<br />\n極速訂閱 黃色頻道<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9viZgif.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9viZgif.gif&h=d9687fce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Cdgu47O1Wlw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCdgu47O1Wlw&d=l2jL6rfoxymyXK22uA%2BdgoICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=5bcc5740\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Cdgu47O1Wlw</a><br />\n［黃藍YOUTUBE大戰正式開打］極簡單方法支持黃YOUTUBER (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1891510\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1891510</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c507b094c589cab77880eb23b61c9e207408cba6","tid":1892400,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:31:30.000Z","msg":"借嚟俾支企做基建<br />\n當地政府冇掂過手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5056fd1f1bf55396fdf808934bbb8e01bd78de87","tid":1892400,"uid":161168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:42:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6425ef0c63f852c34db14e4814bf048fb97a6e08","tid":1892400,"uid":331421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:47:40.000Z","msg":"啲錢落左袋先講"},{"pid":"457b0413e144935d0ad60af001f76ea6a5c599e5","tid":1892400,"uid":141151,"